    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://example.org/ontology#Monitoring"/>
    <hasStewardshipDescription>Maintain adequate fluid intake and urinary output to reduce the possibility of crystalluria. Periodic assessment of renal, hepatic, and hematopoietic functions is recommended during prolonged therapy.</hasStewardshipDescription>
